{"lastModified":1748868755567,"uri":"c::7819307041::vessel::972febe0-3a45-11f0-8f62-01314a7ec29e","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nCruising in Perfect Serenity\n\nIn keeping with the spirit of the line, the Sun Odyssey 440 is a cruising sailboat designed for off-shore sailing. Its resistance, stability, and secure cockpit make it a faithful companion on longer crossings. Careful attention has been paid to fit and finish and to the level of comfort on board – with integrated ventilation, sound insulation, a well-equipped galley, careful selection of materi-als, an exterior sundeck, etc. – to create living spaces dedicated to the enjoyment of life’s simple pleasures and the voyage, itself.\n\nA Sailboat in Your Image\n\nThe Sun Odyssey 440 offers multiple interior layouts: from the version with two immense cabins and a storage locker, to the version with four cabins, able to accommodate up to 10 people, with two in the saloon. For those adept at gentle, perfect manoeuvres, a bow thruster is available. An optional high-performance mast is available to satisfy lovers of speed and performance. And for long-distance sailors, it is possible to integrate a water-maker, solar panels, and additional batteries. Numerous options enable you to configure your boat in function with your needs and preferences.","blueprint":{"name":"ALMYRA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::972febe0-3a45-11f0-8f62-01314a7ec29e::assets::62b830e0-3a48-11f0-8a3b-39fb03fb4c94/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::972febe0-3a45-11f0-8f62-01314a7ec29e::assets::62bb3e20-3a48-11f0-8a3b-39fb03fb4c94/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::972febe0-3a45-11f0-8f62-01314a7ec29e::assets::62aa2720-3a48-11f0-8a3b-39fb03fb4c94/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::972febe0-3a45-11f0-8f62-01314a7ec29e::assets::62b41230-3a48-11f0-8a3b-39fb03fb4c94/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::972febe0-3a45-11f0-8f62-01314a7ec29e::assets::62a8c